\begin{align*} 2x^2 - 52x + 356 &= 2x^2 - 12x + 36 \\ -52x + 356 &= -12x + 36 \\ -40x &= -320 \\ x &= 8 \end{align*}
Then $y = -x+6 = -8+6 = -2$. Thus, $P = (8,-2)$.

